What does this technology (library/framework/service) accomplish for you?
    Path was used for easily joining segments of paths. It solves the problem of us having to type out long paths.

How does this technology accomplish what it does?
    Path basically reads the concatenate strings in a smart way replacing // with \ etc
        Code: https://github.com/jinder/path/blob/master/path.js

What license or terms of service apply to this technology?
    MIT License: https://github.com/jinder/path#license
        This means that we can deploy our web application as normal since MIT License says:

